        <section id="">
            <img id="foodPic" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515003197210-e0cd71810b5f?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjI0MX0&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1050&q=80" alt="">
            <p>The MeMeal food application can be used to find certian foods that you enjoy using a max calorie count per serving while also exluding foods that you have an allergy to. You can save all your favorite foods to your own personalized profile and make adjustments to your favorite meals to make them even better!  </p>

            <div id="loginDiv">
              <form id="loginForm" action="/username" method="POST">
