              </form>
            </div>

        </section>

        <section id="howTo">
            <h2>How to Use</h2>
            <ol>
                <li><span>Step 1:</span> Ensure you are hungry!</li>
                <li><span>Step 2:</span> Login or register depending if you have used the app before</li>
                <li><span>Step 3:</span> If you need to register follow the below registration steps
                    <ul>
                      <li>Click the register link or use the dropdown menu</li>
                      <li>Enter in your profile Username</li>
                      <li>Enter in your daily caloric needs</li>
                      <li>Checkmark any allergies you have</li>
                      <li>Press Save</li>
                      <p>now you can follow the steps for logging in</p>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><span>Step 4:</span> Enter Username and press Login</li>
                <li><span>Step 5:</span> Search, Update, Delete, profile or Recipes</li>
                <li><span>Step 6:</span> When searching a recipe, you can add it to you profile where you can modify all your favorites.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

